  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mental Health Advocacy to improve human rights and reduce poverty of poor people with mental illness and epilepsy in Ashanti and Brong-Ahafo Regions of Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">People with mental illness in Ashanti and Brong-Ahafo Regions of Ghana will satisfy their basic needs and their basic rights will be recognised and respected. The user movement will be strengthened through the formation of 130 self help groups thus enabling people with mental illness and epilepsy to gain confidence, participate in livelihoods and lead advocacy.</narrative>
  </description>
